# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge
We are committed to providing a welcoming and inclusive environment for all contributors and users. We expect everyone to uphold this standard.

## Expected Behavior
- Be respectful and considerate in all interactions.
- Communicate openly and thoughtfully.
- Avoid harassment, discrimination, or abusive language.
- Respect diverse opinions and backgrounds.

## Unacceptable Behavior
- Harassment, intimidation, or discrimination in any form.
- Offensive or exclusionary comments or actions.
- Disruption of the collaborative environment.

## Reporting
If you experience or witness any unacceptable behavior, please report it to the project maintainer at your.email@example.com. All reports will be treated with confidentiality and taken seriously.

## Enforcement
Violations of this Code of Conduct may result in removal from the project or other actions deemed appropriate by the maintainers.

Thank you for helping to create a positive and productive community.
